Anne Fontaine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anne_Fontaine 0 Anne Fontaine (born Anne-Fontaine Sibertin-Blanc; 15 July 1959) is a film director, screenwriter, and former actress. She lives and works in France. Anne_Fontaine ( born Anne-Fontaine_Sibertin-Blanc ; 15_July_1959 ) is a_film_director , screenwriter , and former_actress . She lives_and_works in France .
